WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.700 line:80%
=Episode 20=

00:01:38.290 --> 00:01:39.130 line:80%
Yunke.

00:01:41.420 --> 00:01:42.260 line:80%
Dear?

00:01:43.540 --> 00:01:44.490 line:80%
You came so late.

00:01:44.980 --> 00:01:46.080 line:80%
Is there some urgent matter?

00:01:58.340 --> 00:01:59.930 line:80%
Your affairs are urgent matters.

00:02:00.540 --> 00:02:01.730 line:80%
Ever since you returned,

00:02:01.980 --> 00:02:03.649 line:80%
you have either been busy
with sect duties

00:02:03.660 --> 00:02:05.193 line:80%
or in seclusion regulating your breath.

00:02:05.820 --> 00:02:07.120 line:80%
On this trip,

00:02:07.420 --> 00:02:08.410 line:80%
were you injured?

00:02:08.410 --> 00:02:09.250 line:80%
Dear,

00:02:09.810 --> 00:02:10.650 line:80%
no need to worry.

00:02:10.970 --> 00:02:11.810 line:80%
I have merely

00:02:12.200 --> 00:02:13.260 line:80%
been traveling for days

00:02:13.699 --> 00:02:14.666 line:80%
and am somewhat fatigued.

00:02:17.780 --> 00:02:18.620 line:80%
That is good.

00:02:19.300 --> 00:02:21.460 line:80%
Nanny Mao and I followed
an ancient recipe

00:02:21.460 --> 00:02:22.530 line:80%
to brew a nourishing soup.

00:02:22.970 --> 00:02:24.180 line:80%
It replenishes qi

00:02:24.690 --> 00:02:25.900 line:80%
and helps restore inner power.

00:02:26.580 --> 00:02:28.810 line:80%
I've asked Lingbo
to deliver some to Yuzhi.

00:02:29.340 --> 00:02:30.333 line:80%
Have some while it's hot.

00:02:31.370 --> 00:02:33.620 line:80%
Yuzhi has medicine from Xiuming.

00:02:33.970 --> 00:02:36.020 line:80%
I'm afraid he can't take other remedies.

00:02:36.860 --> 00:02:37.930 line:80%
It doesn't matter.

00:02:37.930 --> 00:02:39.580 line:80%
It's still Lingbo's heartfelt intention.

00:02:40.200 --> 00:02:41.210 line:80%
You don't know.

00:02:41.490 --> 00:02:43.370 line:80%
During the days you
and Yuzhi were away,

00:02:43.690 --> 00:02:45.370 line:80%
Lingbo was deeply worried.

00:02:46.020 --> 00:02:48.210 line:80%
She almost went to look for you,

00:02:48.210 --> 00:02:49.620 line:80%
yet feared she would be of no help,

00:02:49.631 --> 00:02:50.970 line:80%
so she could only wait in anguish.

00:02:52.690 --> 00:02:53.530 line:80%
Thank you, dear.

00:02:54.930 --> 00:02:56.580 line:80%
Lingbo has indeed grown up.

00:02:56.970 --> 00:02:57.810 line:80%
She's sensible now.

00:02:58.140 --> 00:02:59.180 line:80%
She's sensible,

00:02:59.780 --> 00:03:01.420 line:80%
but her thoughts
have also grown heavier.

00:03:02.020 --> 00:03:02.860 line:80%
Yunke,

00:03:03.410 --> 00:03:04.340 line:80%
I know you are busy,

00:03:05.230 --> 00:03:07.010 line:80%
but Lingbo and Yuzhi's marriage

00:03:07.460 --> 00:03:09.210 line:80%
must be prepared sooner or later.

00:03:10.460 --> 00:03:11.690 line:80%
Such a serious matter

00:03:12.410 --> 00:03:13.900 line:80%
should be considered carefully.

00:03:14.370 --> 00:03:15.780 line:80%
What is there to consider?

00:03:16.300 --> 00:03:17.740 line:80%
What a woman seeks in life

00:03:17.740 --> 00:03:19.530 line:80%
is but a thoughtful husband.

00:03:19.530 --> 00:03:21.090 line:80%
Yuzhi is both virtuous and talented,

00:03:21.090 --> 00:03:22.580 line:80%
and he and Lingbo grew up together.

00:03:22.930 --> 00:03:24.900 line:80%
Yuzhi will surely treat Lingbo well.

00:03:26.180 --> 00:03:28.180 line:80%
That requires
both of them to be willing.

00:03:29.340 --> 00:03:31.140 line:80%
Lingbo has admired Yuzhi
since childhood.

00:03:31.460 --> 00:03:32.506 line:80%
Why would she be unwilling?

00:03:36.740 --> 00:03:37.580 line:80%
Dear,

00:03:38.370 --> 00:03:39.300 line:80%
Yuzhi has always had

00:03:39.300 --> 00:03:40.810 line:80%
his own mind.

00:03:41.370 --> 00:03:43.090 line:80%
If I force him,

00:03:43.690 --> 00:03:45.240 line:80%
it may backfire.

00:03:45.740 --> 00:03:47.070 line:80%
Is it that he has his own mind,

00:03:47.740 --> 00:03:48.620 line:80%
or

00:03:49.140 --> 00:03:50.820 line:80%
has his heart belonged to another?

00:03:55.140 --> 00:03:55.980 line:80%
Dear,

00:03:56.690 --> 00:03:57.770 line:80%
what do you mean by that?

00:04:03.690 --> 00:04:04.620 line:80%
I mean,

00:04:05.580 --> 00:04:07.810 line:80%
is he like you were back then?

00:04:09.340 --> 00:04:11.020 line:80%
After spending time with a Cai,

00:04:11.690 --> 00:04:12.930 line:80%
did affection grow with time,

00:04:13.530 --> 00:04:15.410 line:80%
so he forgot his duty

00:04:15.780 --> 00:04:17.460 line:80%
and loved someone else?

00:04:18.730 --> 00:04:19.780 line:80%
I won't drink it.

00:04:20.850 --> 00:04:22.130 line:80%
- Get out.
- Qi Yunke.

00:04:22.780 --> 00:04:24.530 line:80%
Cai Pingshu is dead, not you.

00:04:24.940 --> 00:04:26.780 line:80%
You refuse treatment and medicine,

00:04:26.780 --> 00:04:27.826 line:80%
and you won't speak to me.

00:04:28.210 --> 00:04:29.050 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:04:29.530 --> 00:04:30.370 line:80%
Get out.

00:04:31.610 --> 00:04:32.460 line:80%
Get out of here.

00:04:33.050 --> 00:04:33.900 line:80%
What did you say?

00:04:34.780 --> 00:04:35.780 line:80%
You told me to get out?

00:04:36.500 --> 00:04:37.970 line:80%
Qi Yunke, have you gone mad?

00:04:38.460 --> 00:04:39.850 line:80%
This is Qingque Sect,

00:04:39.850 --> 00:04:40.730 line:80%
not Luoying Valley.

00:04:40.970 --> 00:04:42.290 line:80%
I'm your wife,

00:04:42.290 --> 00:04:43.700 line:80%
the Lord's wife.

00:04:45.090 --> 00:04:46.140 line:80%
The Lord's wife?

00:04:46.700 --> 00:04:48.580 line:80%
It was you who caused Pingshu's death.

00:04:48.580 --> 00:04:49.430 line:80%
It was you!

00:04:49.430 --> 00:04:51.290 line:80%
What does her death have to do with me?

00:04:59.170 --> 00:05:01.780 line:80%
You are my husband.

00:05:03.730 --> 00:05:05.820 line:80%
We've been married for years.

00:05:07.090 --> 00:05:09.850 line:80%
I've done everything I should.

00:05:10.700 --> 00:05:12.970 line:80%
Yet you exhaust yourself
for another woman.

00:05:12.970 --> 00:05:15.940 line:80%
Every time you return,
your cultivation is drained.

00:05:15.940 --> 00:05:17.940 line:80%
I'm merciful enough
not to reason with her.

00:05:18.580 --> 00:05:19.940 line:80%
It's good that she is dead.

00:05:20.380 --> 00:05:21.900 line:80%
You can finally give up.

00:05:23.050 --> 00:05:24.780 line:80%
You no longer need to save her.

00:05:24.780 --> 00:05:25.620 line:80%
I'm useless.

00:05:27.340 --> 00:05:28.180 line:80%
I couldn't save her.

00:05:29.500 --> 00:05:30.820 line:80%
I couldn't!

00:05:33.940 --> 00:05:34.900 line:80%
You are useless.

00:05:36.170 --> 00:05:38.410 line:80%
The Lord of Qingque Sect

00:05:39.020 --> 00:05:41.050 line:80%
is shedding tears
for an unrelated woman.

00:05:41.820 --> 00:05:43.340 line:80%
What righteous light?

00:05:43.850 --> 00:05:45.780 line:80%
What Ms. Cai?

00:05:46.170 --> 00:05:48.140 line:80%
Everyone says Cai Pingshu

00:05:48.140 --> 00:05:49.506 line:80%
fought Nie Hengcheng for the world

00:05:50.170 --> 00:05:53.650 line:80%
until both were gravely wounded.

00:05:53.650 --> 00:05:55.500 line:80%
But I only resent that wretch

00:05:55.500 --> 00:05:56.992 line:80%
for taking so many years to die.

00:05:57.003 --> 00:05:58.140 line:80%
She should've died long ago.

00:05:58.140 --> 00:05:58.980 line:80%
Stop talking.

00:06:00.020 --> 00:06:00.860 line:80%
What?

00:06:01.340 --> 00:06:02.780 line:80%
Instead of wailing here,

00:06:03.210 --> 00:06:04.712 line:80%
you might as well go to Luoying Valley

00:06:04.723 --> 00:06:05.700 line:80%
and be buried with her.

00:06:08.020 --> 00:06:08.860 line:80%
Oh, yes.

00:06:10.290 --> 00:06:11.500 line:80%
I just remembered.

00:06:12.500 --> 00:06:14.210 line:80%
She had Zhou Zhizhen.

00:06:14.210 --> 00:06:16.460 line:80%
She had so many brothers.

00:06:16.460 --> 00:06:17.820 line:80%
It would not even be your turn.

00:06:18.090 --> 00:06:18.930 line:80%
Enough.

00:06:33.780 --> 00:06:34.620 line:80%
Get up.

00:06:40.150 --> 00:06:42.020 line:80%
This ungrateful, filthy place

00:06:43.020 --> 00:06:43.980 line:80%
is not worth staying in.

00:06:44.140 --> 00:06:44.980 line:80%
Let's go.

00:06:48.500 --> 00:06:49.460 line:80%
Wait.

00:06:50.530 --> 00:06:51.530 line:80%
Chang,

00:06:53.210 --> 00:06:54.170 line:80%
I can't leave.

00:06:56.050 --> 00:06:57.700 line:80%
However unbearable this place is,

00:06:59.610 --> 00:07:01.020 line:80%
I must endure it.

00:07:09.170 --> 00:07:10.940 line:80%
Because I'm the Lord.

00:07:20.460 --> 00:07:21.340 line:80%
Lord Qi,

00:07:25.210 --> 00:07:26.050 line:80%
take care.

00:07:55.580 --> 00:07:56.420 line:80%
Dear,

00:07:58.020 --> 00:07:59.090 line:80%
just now,

00:07:59.650 --> 00:08:01.340 line:80%
I had disordered meridians

00:08:02.530 --> 00:08:04.650 line:80%
and nearly fell into deviation.

00:08:07.050 --> 00:08:08.340 line:80%
Please don't blame me.

00:08:15.170 --> 00:08:17.410 line:80%
It seems my obsession is too deep.

00:08:18.050 --> 00:08:20.090 line:80%
Yuzhi has his own ideas.

00:08:20.900 --> 00:08:22.460 line:80%
Once he decides,

00:08:23.020 --> 00:08:24.579 line:80%
he won't easily change.

00:08:24.590 --> 00:08:25.577 line:80%
But do you still remember

00:08:25.588 --> 00:08:27.290 line:80%
what you promised my father
and my sister?

00:08:27.290 --> 00:08:28.410 line:80%
I haven't forgotten.

00:08:28.410 --> 00:08:29.940 line:80%
I promised your father

00:08:30.900 --> 00:08:32.170 line:80%
to take good care of you

00:08:32.780 --> 00:08:34.330 line:80%
and never let you suffer.

00:08:34.330 --> 00:08:35.500 line:80%
I haven't broken that promise.

00:08:35.810 --> 00:08:37.570 line:80%
I also promised your sister

00:08:37.570 --> 00:08:38.860 line:80%
to raise Yuzhi well.

00:08:38.860 --> 00:08:40.330 line:80%
I haven't broken that either.

00:08:40.330 --> 00:08:41.650 line:80%
What about Lingbo?

00:08:41.650 --> 00:08:43.082 line:80%
She's your daughter.

00:08:43.093 --> 00:08:45.129 line:80%
Even if she and Yuzhi
are fated to miss each other,

00:08:45.140 --> 00:08:47.020 line:80%
you should choose
another good husband for her.

00:08:47.020 --> 00:08:48.620 line:80%
Precisely because she is my daughter,

00:08:48.620 --> 00:08:50.410 line:80%
I hope she can

00:08:50.410 --> 00:08:52.290 line:80%
be joyful every day,

00:08:52.290 --> 00:08:53.650 line:80%
rather than forcing herself

00:08:53.650 --> 00:08:54.740 line:80%
into a mistaken marriage.

00:09:30.690 --> 00:09:32.810 line:80%
(Why can't I advance the Ziwei Method?)

00:09:33.780 --> 00:09:34.780 line:80%
(Did I miss something?)

00:09:35.140 --> 00:09:36.140 line:80%
(The Ziwei Method.)

00:09:37.050 --> 00:09:38.290 line:80%
(Take the resilience of gold.)

00:09:38.570 --> 00:09:39.740 line:80%
(Take the firmness of jade.)

00:09:40.170 --> 00:09:41.290 line:80%
(Refine bones with gold.)

00:09:41.570 --> 00:09:42.900 line:80%
(Temper the heart with jade.)

00:09:43.410 --> 00:09:44.780 line:80%
This Jade Sunflower

00:09:44.780 --> 00:09:46.650 line:80%
is merely a healing item

00:09:46.650 --> 00:09:48.780 line:80%
to calm the mind and warm the meridians.

00:09:48.780 --> 00:09:50.690 line:80%
Why would Nie Hengcheng value it so much

00:09:51.570 --> 00:09:53.930 line:80%
that he'd injure his trusted disciple?

00:09:53.930 --> 00:09:56.690 line:80%
Lu Chengnan was even the next chief.

00:09:57.220 --> 00:09:58.980 line:80%
Why offend Nie Hengcheng

00:09:59.380 --> 00:10:00.810 line:80%
over a mere object?

00:10:01.860 --> 00:10:02.810 line:80%
The Jade Sunflower.

00:10:09.530 --> 00:10:10.620 line:80%
Greetings, Young Master.

00:10:13.823 --> 00:10:15.403 line:80%
I called you here for nothing important.

00:10:16.100 --> 00:10:17.046 line:80%
I only wish to ask

00:10:17.057 --> 00:10:18.446 line:80%
what you plan to do in the future.

00:10:18.620 --> 00:10:19.860 line:80%
You're merciful.

00:10:21.250 --> 00:10:22.930 line:80%
Si'en and I are deeply grateful.

00:10:23.530 --> 00:10:24.650 line:80%
After we leave this time,

00:10:24.650 --> 00:10:26.453 line:80%
we'll find a secluded village

00:10:26.464 --> 00:10:27.966 line:80%
and spend the rest of our lives there,

00:10:28.650 --> 00:10:30.980 line:80%
never again entangled with Li Sect.

00:10:33.380 --> 00:10:34.220 line:80%
Rise.

00:10:36.620 --> 00:10:38.530 line:80%
We don't have freedom in Jianghu.

00:10:38.886 --> 00:10:40.312 line:80%
Love and hatred are hard to sever.

00:10:40.450 --> 00:10:41.980 line:80%
My father also once wished

00:10:43.020 --> 00:10:44.810 line:80%
to live alone
and pass his days in peace.

00:10:45.690 --> 00:10:46.930 line:80%
I still remember back then,

00:10:46.930 --> 00:10:48.330 line:80%
my father was on good terms

00:10:48.330 --> 00:10:50.410 line:80%
with you and Lu Chengnan.

00:10:50.410 --> 00:10:51.740 line:80%
I wonder whether Elder Lu

00:10:53.450 --> 00:10:54.570 line:80%
is still alive.

00:10:55.450 --> 00:10:56.290 line:80%
Yes.

00:10:56.980 --> 00:10:59.290 line:80%
There has been no news of Lu
for a long time.

00:10:59.780 --> 00:11:01.100 line:80%
Among the many elders of Li Sect,

00:11:01.960 --> 00:11:03.930 line:80%
Elder Lu was the most loyal and brave.

00:11:04.530 --> 00:11:05.690 line:80%
Yet his whole life

00:11:06.140 --> 00:11:07.413 line:80%
was trapped by those two words.

00:11:07.810 --> 00:11:09.020 line:80%
After he left,

00:11:09.570 --> 00:11:11.130 line:80%
my foster father's temperament changed.

00:11:11.450 --> 00:11:12.900 line:80%
Everyone was overwhelmed.

00:11:13.290 --> 00:11:15.170 line:80%
There were no more banquets in the sect,

00:11:15.170 --> 00:11:18.050 line:80%
no more music from Mr. Mu Zhengming,

00:11:19.100 --> 00:11:20.650 line:80%
nor the fragrance of the Osmanthus Wine

00:11:20.650 --> 00:11:23.140 line:80%
Lu loved most.

00:11:26.740 --> 00:11:27.740 line:80%
Osmanthus Wine?

00:11:30.050 --> 00:11:31.050 line:80%
It's late.

00:11:32.410 --> 00:11:33.530 line:80%
Go back and rest early.

00:11:33.930 --> 00:11:34.780 line:80%
Take care.

00:11:34.780 --> 00:11:35.810 line:80%
Take care, Young Master.

00:11:54.050 --> 00:11:55.140 line:80%
Osmanthus Wine.

00:11:58.100 --> 00:11:59.930 line:80%
The company of osmanthus flowers now

00:12:00.690 --> 00:12:02.380 line:80%
will never match the days of youth.

00:12:04.300 --> 00:12:05.540 line:80%
(Osmanthus Wine)
Cheers.

00:12:08.900 --> 00:12:11.290 line:80%
(Could the old friend
Mr. Chang was honoring)

00:12:11.290 --> 00:12:12.500 line:80%
(be Lu Chengnan?)

00:12:14.860 --> 00:12:15.700 line:80%
Young Master.

00:12:17.690 --> 00:12:18.530 line:80%
Young Master.

00:12:19.220 --> 00:12:20.060 line:80%
What is it?

00:12:20.110 --> 00:12:20.980 line:80%
Young Master,

00:12:20.990 --> 00:12:22.380 line:80%
you can't let Miss Cai get married.

00:12:22.900 --> 00:12:23.810 line:80%
Married?

00:12:23.810 --> 00:12:25.380 line:80%
It's said Qi Yunke

00:12:25.380 --> 00:12:26.740 line:80%
is preparing a wedding

00:12:26.740 --> 00:12:27.860 line:80%
for Miss Cai and Zhou.

00:12:27.860 --> 00:12:28.980 line:80%
I asked Shangguan.

00:12:28.980 --> 00:12:30.050 line:80%
The Thousandfold Cliff

00:12:30.050 --> 00:12:31.500 line:80%
is not iron.

00:12:31.500 --> 00:12:32.390 line:80%
Why don't we

00:12:32.390 --> 00:12:33.740 line:80%
storm Qingque Sect directly

00:12:33.740 --> 00:12:35.020 line:80%
and snatch Miss Cai back?

00:12:36.410 --> 00:12:38.620 line:80%
She'll marry Zhou Yuqi?

00:12:38.900 --> 00:12:40.380 line:80%
I don't even know

00:12:40.810 --> 00:12:42.050 line:80%
where this Zhou Yuqi came from.

00:12:42.570 --> 00:12:44.330 line:80%
I can accept Mr. Song.

00:12:44.330 --> 00:12:45.170 line:80%
But Zhou...

00:12:57.780 --> 00:12:59.650 line:80%
Why cry while embroidering?

00:13:03.500 --> 00:13:05.140 line:80%
You're about to marry.

00:13:05.810 --> 00:13:07.410 line:80%
I'm happy, so I want

00:13:07.410 --> 00:13:09.100 line:80%
to embroider two mandarin ducks for you.

00:13:10.290 --> 00:13:11.620 line:80%
But when I think

00:13:11.836 --> 00:13:13.489 line:80%
that after Miss Cai becomes
the mistress,

00:13:14.810 --> 00:13:15.860 line:80%
we'll never again have

00:13:15.860 --> 00:13:17.100 line:80%
such days as these,

00:13:17.740 --> 00:13:18.810 line:80%
I can't bear it.

00:13:21.290 --> 00:13:22.130 line:80%
Xinrou.

00:13:27.450 --> 00:13:28.780 line:80%
All right, don't cry.

00:13:29.100 --> 00:13:30.100 line:80%
Zhao is gentle.

00:13:30.100 --> 00:13:31.410 line:80%
She won't cast you aside.

00:13:32.330 --> 00:13:34.380 line:80%
Just stay in the manor at ease.

00:13:34.900 --> 00:13:35.740 line:80%
All right?

00:13:36.530 --> 00:13:37.370 line:80%
Don't cry.

00:14:03.050 --> 00:14:03.890 line:80%
Why did Aunt

00:14:04.650 --> 00:14:06.740 line:80%
give up Uncle Zhou back then?

00:14:09.410 --> 00:14:11.140 line:80%
Was it because
of the skin-painted demon?

00:14:15.690 --> 00:14:16.530 line:80%
Zhao,

00:14:16.810 --> 00:14:17.980 line:80%
in all matters, do your best

00:14:17.980 --> 00:14:19.140 line:80%
and follow your heart.

00:14:20.170 --> 00:14:21.740 line:80%
My mother once said

00:14:21.740 --> 00:14:23.380 line:80%
that choices are the hardest to make.

00:14:23.380 --> 00:14:25.220 line:80%
Listen carefully
to the voice in your heart,

00:14:25.810 --> 00:14:27.330 line:80%
and you will know what to do.

00:14:31.330 --> 00:14:32.290 line:80%
Are you hurt?

00:14:38.410 --> 00:14:40.050 line:80%
I don't think I want to marry Yuqi.

00:14:55.860 --> 00:14:58.570 line:80%
The Sunflower might've been taken
to the Chang clan by Lu Chengnan.

00:14:58.570 --> 00:15:00.690 line:80%
The massacre may be related to him.

00:15:02.220 --> 00:15:03.913 line:80%
(The Jade Sunflower
is at the Chang clan?)

00:15:16.620 --> 00:15:18.530 line:80%
Red beans on an exquisite dice.

00:15:20.380 --> 00:15:23.220 line:80%
Do you know I'm missing you?

00:15:25.020 --> 00:15:26.106 line:80%
I don't care who you miss.

00:15:34.620 --> 00:15:35.460 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:15:37.170 --> 00:15:38.010 line:80%
Zhao.

00:15:41.290 --> 00:15:43.290 line:80%
Lu Chengnan was
Nie Hengcheng's trusted disciple.

00:15:43.290 --> 00:15:45.330 line:80%
So, Mu Qingyan likely spoke the truth.

00:15:45.650 --> 00:15:46.490 line:80%
Zhao,

00:15:46.980 --> 00:15:48.013 line:80%
do you wish to verify it?

00:15:48.140 --> 00:15:49.900 line:80%
Don't you also need the Jade Sunflower?

00:15:51.410 --> 00:15:52.690 line:80%
But the mechanisms of Chang Fort

00:15:52.690 --> 00:15:54.100 line:80%
were set by my aunt.

00:15:54.100 --> 00:15:55.633 line:80%
Lu Chengnan was a demonic disciple.

00:15:55.644 --> 00:15:56.677 line:80%
How could he have entered?

00:15:58.050 --> 00:15:59.470 line:80%
Thinking back to the investigation,

00:15:59.650 --> 00:16:00.620 line:80%
I think it was rushed.

00:16:01.290 --> 00:16:02.330 line:80%
Yuzhi, do you think

00:16:02.810 --> 00:16:03.972 line:80%
there was anything suspicious

00:16:03.983 --> 00:16:05.450 line:80%
we overlooked?

00:16:05.450 --> 00:16:07.330 line:80%
For example, a hidden passage
or secret chamber

00:16:07.330 --> 00:16:08.170 line:80%
we never discovered?

00:16:08.650 --> 00:16:09.490 line:80%
Zhao.

00:16:11.530 --> 00:16:12.370 line:80%
Master.

00:16:12.620 --> 00:16:13.460 line:80%
What are you

00:16:13.980 --> 00:16:15.500 line:80%
discussing so early in the morning?

00:16:15.930 --> 00:16:17.590 line:80%
Yuzhi and I were talking

00:16:17.601 --> 00:16:19.020 line:80%
about the mechanisms of Chang Fort.

00:16:19.020 --> 00:16:19.860 line:80%
Master,

00:16:20.140 --> 00:16:22.450 line:80%
Mr. Chang's death anniversary is near.

00:16:22.450 --> 00:16:25.140 line:80%
I witnessed the tragic scene.

00:16:25.140 --> 00:16:26.810 line:80%
Even now, my heart still aches.

00:16:27.220 --> 00:16:28.780 line:80%
So, I wish to go with Zhao

00:16:28.780 --> 00:16:29.900 line:80%
to pay our respects.

00:16:31.170 --> 00:16:32.140 line:80%
As it should be.

00:16:33.300 --> 00:16:35.220 line:80%
If I were not entangled in sect affairs,

00:16:35.450 --> 00:16:36.450 line:80%
I would go with you.

00:16:37.130 --> 00:16:38.050 line:80%
It's fine, Master.

00:16:38.780 --> 00:16:40.500 line:80%
Yuzhi and I

00:16:40.500 --> 00:16:42.530 line:80%
can offer incense on your behalf.

00:16:45.410 --> 00:16:46.250 line:80%
Very well.

00:16:53.980 --> 00:16:55.810 line:80%
Master, no need to see us off.

00:16:55.810 --> 00:16:57.050 line:80%
It's only a few steps.

00:16:57.050 --> 00:16:58.050 line:80%
It's no trouble.

00:16:58.050 --> 00:16:59.690 line:80%
The scenery is best in this season.

00:17:00.100 --> 00:17:01.530 line:80%
You may stroll around as well.

00:17:03.500 --> 00:17:04.340 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:17:05.570 --> 00:17:07.420 line:80%
in this bundle, there are banknotes

00:17:07.850 --> 00:17:10.780 line:80%
and some hairpins and bracelets
that girls favor.

00:17:11.530 --> 00:17:13.050 line:80%
Find a time to give them to Zhao.

00:17:14.050 --> 00:17:14.940 line:80%
Father,

00:17:15.180 --> 00:17:16.473 line:80%
we're going to pay our respects.

00:17:17.180 --> 00:17:18.020 line:80%
I know.

00:17:18.500 --> 00:17:19.780 line:80%
Take care of yourself, Master.

00:17:20.460 --> 00:17:22.460 line:80%
Don't let me worry while away.

00:17:22.460 --> 00:17:23.330 line:80%
You too.

00:17:24.020 --> 00:17:25.050 line:80%
When outside,

00:17:25.050 --> 00:17:26.290 line:80%
be cautious in all matters.

00:17:27.810 --> 00:17:29.180 line:80%
Mr. Chang

00:17:29.180 --> 00:17:30.610 line:80%
was righteous and loyal.

00:17:30.610 --> 00:17:32.370 line:80%
You must pay your respects properly.

00:17:32.660 --> 00:17:33.500 line:80%
Zhao,

00:17:33.700 --> 00:17:35.020 line:80%
it's a long journey.

00:17:35.193 --> 00:17:36.489 line:80%
If you need anything on the road,

00:17:36.500 --> 00:17:37.530 line:80%
have this lad run errands.

00:17:37.980 --> 00:17:39.530 line:80%
Don't treat him as an outsider.

00:17:39.530 --> 00:17:40.980 line:80%
Don't worry, Uncle Song.

00:17:40.980 --> 00:17:42.420 line:80%
We'll return in ten days.

00:17:42.420 --> 00:17:43.700 line:80%
I'll take good care of Zhao.

00:17:44.220 --> 00:17:45.850 line:80%
Good. You finally understand.

00:17:45.850 --> 00:17:47.090 line:80%
All right, enough chatter.

00:17:47.090 --> 00:17:48.420 line:80%
Let them set off.

00:17:48.420 --> 00:17:49.260 line:80%
Go on.

00:17:49.460 --> 00:17:50.570 line:80%
Yes, Master.

00:17:50.940 --> 00:17:51.780 line:80%
Go.

00:17:52.610 --> 00:17:53.450 line:80%
Wait.

00:17:55.130 --> 00:17:55.970 line:80%
Wait a moment.

00:17:57.493 --> 00:17:58.980 line:80%
- Why are you all here?
- We made it.

00:17:58.980 --> 00:18:00.290 line:80%
Why carry bundles to see them off?

00:18:00.810 --> 00:18:01.650 line:80%
Uncle.

00:18:01.890 --> 00:18:02.740 line:80%
Father,

00:18:02.740 --> 00:18:05.090 line:80%
don't you always say
I should travel more in Jianghu

00:18:05.090 --> 00:18:06.020 line:80%
to broaden my horizons?

00:18:06.020 --> 00:18:08.090 line:80%
Since Cai Zhao is going to pay respects,

00:18:08.090 --> 00:18:09.290 line:80%
I wish to go as well

00:18:09.290 --> 00:18:10.130 line:80%
and gain experience.

00:18:10.500 --> 00:18:11.740 line:80%
Lingbo lacks experience.

00:18:11.740 --> 00:18:12.810 line:80%
I'll accompany her.

00:18:12.810 --> 00:18:14.050 line:80%
I've long admired

00:18:14.050 --> 00:18:15.180 line:80%
the Chang's Willow Sword.

00:18:15.180 --> 00:18:17.220 line:80%
I wish to pay my respects
at Mr. Chang's grave.

00:18:17.980 --> 00:18:19.212 line:80%
- You...
- Master,

00:18:19.223 --> 00:18:20.660 line:80%
if my senior brothers go without me,

00:18:20.660 --> 00:18:22.350 line:80%
they may not even
settle accounts clearly.

00:18:22.361 --> 00:18:24.330 line:80%
Let me join to honor Mr. Chang.

00:18:26.030 --> 00:18:28.490 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills♪

00:18:28.490 --> 00:18:29.800 line:80%
♪In the martial world♪

00:18:29.850 --> 00:18:31.050 line:80%
It must be a hard journey.

00:18:31.500 --> 00:18:32.660 line:80%
Let me go on your behalf

00:18:32.660 --> 00:18:34.660 line:80%
and pay respects,

00:18:35.220 --> 00:18:36.130 line:80%
Yuqi, Xinrou.

00:18:36.130 --> 00:18:36.990 line:80%
Zhao,

00:18:37.000 --> 00:18:39.130 line:80%
I'm escorting my cousin back.
It's on the way.

00:18:39.130 --> 00:18:39.970 line:80%
It's no trouble.

00:18:41.940 --> 00:18:43.180 line:80%
Father,

00:18:43.180 --> 00:18:44.660 line:80%
please let us go.

00:18:44.660 --> 00:18:45.980 line:80%
- Please.
- Please.

00:18:45.980 --> 00:18:46.850 line:80%
Yes, Master.

00:18:46.850 --> 00:18:47.980 line:80%
Very well.

00:18:47.980 --> 00:18:50.050 line:80%
Travel together
and don't waste your youth.

00:18:50.050 --> 00:18:50.890 line:80%
Go on.

00:18:51.460 --> 00:18:52.420 line:80%
All right then.

00:18:54.303 --> 00:18:55.700 line:80%
- Thanks, Father.
- Thanks, Master.

00:18:55.700 --> 00:18:56.540 line:80%
Let's go.

00:18:56.780 --> 00:18:57.980 line:80%
- Thanks, Master.
- Go.

00:18:57.980 --> 00:19:02.970 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:19:07.610 --> 00:19:08.530 line:80%
Look.

00:19:08.530 --> 00:19:09.850 line:80%
So many third wheels.

00:19:10.940 --> 00:19:11.890 line:80%
I think so.

00:19:12.330 --> 00:19:13.890 line:80%
How troublesome.

00:19:13.890 --> 00:19:15.890 line:80%
Then why did you not stop them?

00:19:15.890 --> 00:19:17.330 line:80%
You did not stop them either.

00:19:17.330 --> 00:19:18.170 line:80%
You...

00:19:23.940 --> 00:19:24.850 line:80%
Zhao,

00:19:24.850 --> 00:19:26.050 line:80%
Xinrou has caught a chill.

00:19:26.189 --> 00:19:27.742 line:80%
I'll take her to see a physician first.

00:19:28.050 --> 00:19:29.420 line:80%
We'll join you later.

00:19:29.810 --> 00:19:31.330 line:80%
Yuqi, farewell.

00:19:31.330 --> 00:19:32.780 line:80%
Zhao, farewell.

00:19:56.090 --> 00:19:56.930 line:80%
We've arrived.

00:19:59.980 --> 00:20:02.420 line:80%
(Chang Fort)

00:20:30.130 --> 00:20:30.970 line:80%
Chang Ning?

00:20:31.740 --> 00:20:32.740 line:80%
I'm Mu Qingyan

00:20:33.780 --> 00:20:34.850 line:80%
of Li Sect.

00:20:36.780 --> 00:20:37.980 line:80%
The new Chief.

00:20:38.660 --> 00:20:39.940 line:80%
I knew long ago you were a fake.

00:20:40.610 --> 00:20:42.130 line:80%
You schemed to hide in Qingque Sect.

00:20:42.130 --> 00:20:43.220 line:80%
What was your intention?

00:20:43.740 --> 00:20:44.660 line:80%
The Young Master came

00:20:44.660 --> 00:20:46.130 line:80%
to honor an old friend.

00:20:46.530 --> 00:20:48.130 line:80%
We don't wish to stir trouble.

00:20:48.810 --> 00:20:50.700 line:80%
Everyone, no need to be tense.

00:20:50.700 --> 00:20:51.266 line:80%
Nonsense.

00:20:51.354 --> 00:20:53.050 line:80%
The demonic sect massacred
the Chang clan.

00:20:53.050 --> 00:20:54.020 line:80%
What old friend?

00:20:54.020 --> 00:20:54.940 line:80%
Enough talk.

00:20:55.530 --> 00:20:56.460 line:80%
Make your move.

00:20:57.500 --> 00:20:58.340 line:80%
Mr. Mu,

00:21:13.780 --> 00:21:15.126 line:80%
since you don't wish for conflict,

00:21:15.330 --> 00:21:16.170 line:80%
words are useless.

00:21:17.530 --> 00:21:18.460 line:80%
Let's part here.

00:21:34.890 --> 00:21:35.730 line:80%
Let's go.

00:21:52.420 --> 00:21:54.580 line:80%
(Wu'an Inn)

00:21:54.580 --> 00:21:58.540 line:80%
(Wu'an Town)

00:22:06.700 --> 00:22:07.980 line:80%
(Kind and Hospitable)

00:22:07.980 --> 00:22:09.370 line:80%
The anniversary is in three days.

00:22:10.050 --> 00:22:10.996 line:80%
Let's stay here first.

00:22:11.530 --> 00:22:13.500 line:80%
Notify Taichu Temple nearby
to heighten vigilance.

00:22:14.570 --> 00:22:15.410 line:80%
Cai Zhao,

00:22:16.420 --> 00:22:18.220 line:80%
you knew he was the demonic sect chief.

00:22:18.220 --> 00:22:19.370 line:80%
Why let him go?

00:22:19.980 --> 00:22:21.050 line:80%
I can't defeat him.

00:22:21.050 --> 00:22:22.290 line:80%
You can't defeat him?

00:22:22.290 --> 00:22:23.810 line:80%
I think it's not that you can't,

00:22:23.810 --> 00:22:25.330 line:80%
but that you were colluding all along.

00:22:25.850 --> 00:22:27.330 line:80%
Back in Qingque Sect,

00:22:27.330 --> 00:22:28.740 line:80%
you lived together every day.

00:22:30.700 --> 00:22:33.220 line:80%
Zhao must've been deceived by him.

00:22:33.220 --> 00:22:34.780 line:80%
Who deceived whom?

00:22:34.780 --> 00:22:37.020 line:80%
They went in and out together back then.

00:22:37.020 --> 00:22:38.610 line:80%
Cai Zhao defended him time and again.

00:22:38.610 --> 00:22:39.450 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:22:39.610 --> 00:22:41.290 line:80%
if you hadn't bullied Chang then,

00:22:41.740 --> 00:22:43.180 line:80%
why would Zhao have stayed with him?

00:22:43.660 --> 00:22:44.610 line:80%
- You...
- Yuzhi,

00:22:44.610 --> 00:22:45.649 line:80%
Lingbo was insightful

00:22:45.660 --> 00:22:47.513 line:80%
and discovered
that Chang Ning was suspicious.

00:22:48.050 --> 00:22:49.780 line:80%
We shouldn't have let that demon go.

00:22:49.780 --> 00:22:50.620 line:80%
We can't defeat him.

00:22:52.810 --> 00:22:54.090 line:80%
The two men Mu Qingyan brought

00:22:54.560 --> 00:22:55.082 line:80%
had sealed

00:22:55.093 --> 00:22:56.940 line:80%
all our attacking angles
with their positions.

00:22:56.940 --> 00:22:57.780 line:80%
Within 100 moves,

00:22:57.940 --> 00:22:59.186 line:80%
we couldn't have subdued them.

00:22:59.780 --> 00:23:00.890 line:80%
If we truly fought,

00:23:00.890 --> 00:23:02.036 line:80%
we had no chance of victory.

00:23:03.810 --> 00:23:04.650 line:80%
Enough.

00:23:05.090 --> 00:23:06.076 line:80%
We are weary from travel.

00:23:06.530 --> 00:23:07.660 line:80%
Let's rest today.

00:23:08.180 --> 00:23:09.050 line:80%
Boring.

00:23:09.050 --> 00:23:09.890 line:80%
Lingbo.

00:23:14.510 --> 00:23:15.370 line:80%
Lingbo.

00:23:15.370 --> 00:23:16.210 line:80%
Stop calling me.

00:23:16.660 --> 00:23:18.050 line:80%
Weary from travel?

00:23:18.290 --> 00:23:19.263 line:80%
As if he alone is tired.

00:23:23.780 --> 00:23:24.620 line:80%
Zhuo,

00:23:25.420 --> 00:23:28.130 line:80%
I did not see any positioning.

00:23:28.570 --> 00:23:30.570 line:80%
Were they not just standing there?

00:23:31.090 --> 00:23:33.290 line:80%
But their clothing fabric looked fine.

00:23:33.290 --> 00:23:34.530 line:80%
Not found in the market.

00:23:34.530 --> 00:23:35.850 line:80%
The style was novel too.

00:23:35.850 --> 00:23:37.980 line:80%
The demonic sect's tailoring

00:23:38.420 --> 00:23:39.260 line:80%
is truly impressive.

00:23:39.850 --> 00:23:41.290 line:80%
You only noticed their clothes?

00:23:42.813 --> 00:23:44.166 line:80%
Yes, I only noticed their clothes.

00:23:46.460 --> 00:23:48.263 line:80%
I know Mr. Mu is not a bad person.

00:23:48.274 --> 00:23:50.039 line:80%
- But we're...
- We're not on the same side.

00:23:50.050 --> 00:23:50.890 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:23:51.370 --> 00:23:52.220 line:80%
I know what to do.

00:24:24.780 --> 00:24:26.050 line:80%
You've finally arrived.

00:24:26.736 --> 00:24:27.849 line:80%
I've waited for a long time.

00:24:31.130 --> 00:24:32.850 line:80%
How did you bribe the innkeeper?

00:24:34.660 --> 00:24:35.810 line:80%
I did not bribe him.

00:24:38.090 --> 00:24:39.570 line:80%
I bought the entire inn.

00:24:39.890 --> 00:24:41.570 line:80%
This is the only inn in Wu'an Town.

00:24:42.220 --> 00:24:43.420 line:80%
If you came,

00:24:43.890 --> 00:24:44.850 line:80%
you'd have to stay here.

00:24:49.810 --> 00:24:51.530 line:80%
Don't make futile plans.

00:24:52.370 --> 00:24:53.850 line:80%
After I pay respects to Uncle Chang,

00:24:53.850 --> 00:24:55.020 line:80%
I'll return to Qingque Sect.

00:24:55.020 --> 00:24:56.290 line:80%
And marry Zhou Yuqi?

00:24:59.330 --> 00:25:01.090 line:80%
Such a weak and useless man

00:25:01.660 --> 00:25:02.940 line:80%
can catch your eye?

00:25:03.940 --> 00:25:05.360 line:80%
As I recall, you told me last time

00:25:05.420 --> 00:25:07.850 line:80%
not to meddle in demonic sect affairs.

00:25:08.810 --> 00:25:09.802 line:80%
Then you shouldn't meddle

00:25:09.813 --> 00:25:11.483 line:80%
in the affairs of our Six Sects, either.

00:25:16.130 --> 00:25:17.420 line:80%
You've traveled all day.

00:25:18.780 --> 00:25:19.620 line:80%
Are you hungry?

00:25:30.280 --> 00:25:31.566 line:80%
These just came out of the pot.

00:25:31.980 --> 00:25:32.820 line:80%
Eat while hot.

00:25:33.420 --> 00:25:35.090 line:80%
If left too long,

00:25:35.090 --> 00:25:36.090 line:80%
the skin will turn soggy.

00:26:09.090 --> 00:26:09.930 line:80%
Shangguan,

00:26:10.106 --> 00:26:11.772 line:80%
do you think Miss Cai
and the Young Master

00:26:11.810 --> 00:26:12.660 line:80%
are fighting,

00:26:12.813 --> 00:26:14.282 line:80%
or reuniting after a long separation,

00:26:14.366 --> 00:26:15.492 line:80%
or full of tender affection?

00:26:16.420 --> 00:26:17.740 line:80%
A gentleman does not pry.

00:26:18.460 --> 00:26:19.890 line:80%
Master You, you are too nosy.

00:26:21.500 --> 00:26:22.340 line:80%
If you are not nosy,

00:26:22.740 --> 00:26:23.786 line:80%
why are you standing here?

00:26:24.050 --> 00:26:25.570 line:80%
The Young Master may be in danger.

00:26:25.763 --> 00:26:26.903 line:80%
I'm protecting him in secret.

00:26:34.420 --> 00:26:35.260 line:80%
Tell me.

00:26:35.696 --> 00:26:37.815 line:80%
What was the relationship
between Lu and Uncle Chang?

00:26:38.420 --> 00:26:40.020 line:80%
Why did they bring the Jade Sunflower

00:26:40.020 --> 00:26:41.050 line:80%
to Chang Fort?

00:26:42.180 --> 00:26:43.453 line:80%
After you answer, you may leave.

00:26:44.056 --> 00:26:45.700 line:80%
Others grow soft
after eating one's food.

00:26:45.700 --> 00:26:46.850 line:80%
Yet with you,

00:26:46.850 --> 00:26:48.370 line:80%
you turn hostile before swallowing.

00:26:48.940 --> 00:26:51.090 line:80%
You truly are different.

00:26:52.020 --> 00:26:52.860 line:80%
Forget it then.

00:26:53.530 --> 00:26:54.370 line:80%
I'll tell you.

00:26:57.740 --> 00:26:59.290 line:80%
I deduced it

00:26:59.290 --> 00:27:00.330 line:80%
through Osmanthus Wine.

00:27:00.733 --> 00:27:02.740 line:80%
Before his death,
Mr. Chang brought Osmanthus Wine

00:27:02.740 --> 00:27:04.166 line:80%
to pay respects to an old friend.

00:27:04.610 --> 00:27:05.570 line:80%
And the wine

00:27:06.180 --> 00:27:07.530 line:80%
Lu Chengnan loved most

00:27:08.090 --> 00:27:09.180 line:80%
was Osmanthus Wine.

00:27:09.940 --> 00:27:10.780 line:80%
That is all?

00:27:12.000 --> 00:27:13.840 line:80%
Many in this world

00:27:14.290 --> 00:27:15.290 line:80%
love Osmanthus Wine.

00:27:15.740 --> 00:27:16.660 line:80%
Of course.

00:27:17.980 --> 00:27:19.810 line:80%
Before dying,

00:27:20.382 --> 00:27:21.508 line:80%
Mr. Chang repeatedly told me

00:27:21.980 --> 00:27:24.180 line:80%
the massacre was not aimed at me.

00:27:25.330 --> 00:27:26.610 line:80%
He told me not to feel indebted.

00:27:27.570 --> 00:27:29.220 line:80%
I always thought

00:27:29.220 --> 00:27:30.500 line:80%
he was merely comforting me.

00:27:31.050 --> 00:27:32.220 line:80%
But now I think

00:27:32.980 --> 00:27:34.980 line:80%
he may have spoken the truth.

00:27:35.890 --> 00:27:36.730 line:80%
The Chang clan

00:27:37.420 --> 00:27:38.700 line:80%
was hiding a secret.

00:27:40.250 --> 00:27:42.156 line:80%
Could it be that after Lu
was gravely injured,

00:27:43.220 --> 00:27:44.980 line:80%
he fled to Chang Fort?

00:27:44.980 --> 00:27:47.020 line:80%
The men in black dug through the fort.

00:27:49.370 --> 00:27:50.780 line:80%
I believe they were searching

00:27:51.740 --> 00:27:54.130 line:80%
for the Jade Sunflower
Lu Chengnan had taken.

00:27:54.610 --> 00:27:55.500 line:80%
The Jade Sunflower

00:27:55.500 --> 00:27:57.610 line:80%
is used to dispel cold.

00:27:57.610 --> 00:27:59.443 line:80%
Why would they go
to such lengths to find it,

00:28:00.130 --> 00:28:01.850 line:80%
even exterminating the Chang clan?

00:28:05.130 --> 00:28:06.370 line:80%
The exact reason

00:28:06.370 --> 00:28:07.460 line:80%
is unknown for now.

00:28:09.090 --> 00:28:11.130 line:80%
But since the men in black
did not find it,

00:28:11.500 --> 00:28:13.330 line:80%
it must still be in Chang Fort.

00:28:14.700 --> 00:28:16.290 line:80%
How do you know they did not find it?

00:28:16.700 --> 00:28:17.940 line:80%
If they had,

00:28:18.660 --> 00:28:20.180 line:80%
they wouldn't have gone to such trouble

00:28:20.180 --> 00:28:22.290 line:80%
to abduct Chang Ning at Qingque Sect.

00:28:24.290 --> 00:28:25.130 line:80%
Zhao,

00:28:25.940 --> 00:28:27.290 line:80%
when you returned to Qingque Sect,

00:28:27.980 --> 00:28:30.290 line:80%
did you tell everything truthfully?

00:28:31.810 --> 00:28:32.650 line:80%
Did Lord Qi

00:28:34.330 --> 00:28:35.740 line:80%
say anything about me?

00:28:37.020 --> 00:28:39.020 line:80%
He said you are a skin-painted demon,

00:28:39.700 --> 00:28:41.330 line:80%
wearing human skin convincingly,

00:28:41.660 --> 00:28:43.100 line:80%
but destined to devour hearts.

00:28:43.420 --> 00:28:44.460 line:80%
I'm a skin-painted demon?

00:28:50.050 --> 00:28:51.180 line:80%
If I'm a skin-painted demon,

00:28:52.330 --> 00:28:53.290 line:80%
what are they?

00:28:54.890 --> 00:28:56.370 line:80%
After the Chang massacre,

00:28:56.700 --> 00:28:57.820 line:80%
besides your Luoying Valley,

00:28:58.370 --> 00:28:59.780 line:80%
which of the other five sects

00:28:59.780 --> 00:29:02.370 line:80%
truly wanted to avenge the Changs?

00:29:03.530 --> 00:29:04.570 line:80%
They are all hypocrites.

00:29:05.610 --> 00:29:06.660 line:80%
Even Lord Qi...

00:29:11.570 --> 00:29:12.460 line:80%
Those two

00:29:12.810 --> 00:29:13.730 line:80%
have reconciled again?

00:29:14.130 --> 00:29:15.500 line:80%
The Young Master is mighty.

00:29:15.850 --> 00:29:17.940 line:80%
Subduing Li Sect followers
is nothing to him,

00:29:18.330 --> 00:29:19.170 line:80%
let alone Miss Cai.

00:29:20.290 --> 00:29:21.290 line:80%
I would not even bother

00:29:21.570 --> 00:29:22.483 line:80%
to utter such flattery.

00:29:25.460 --> 00:29:27.700 line:80%
Speaking ill of my elders? Get out.

00:29:28.850 --> 00:29:29.780 line:80%
What is happening?

00:29:30.330 --> 00:29:31.420 line:80%
Are they arguing again?

00:29:31.750 --> 00:29:32.970 line:80%
From my understanding of women,

00:29:33.570 --> 00:29:34.530 line:80%
it should be

00:29:34.530 --> 00:29:35.530 line:80%
the Young Master

00:29:36.220 --> 00:29:37.060 line:80%
being scolded.

00:29:46.610 --> 00:29:47.676 line:80%
Good evening, Young Master.

00:29:48.700 --> 00:29:50.610 line:80%
Such leisure...

00:29:50.610 --> 00:29:51.650 line:80%
Are you admiring the moon?

00:29:59.090 --> 00:30:00.090 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:30:00.660 --> 00:30:02.050 line:80%
how carefree of you

00:30:02.330 --> 00:30:03.180 line:80%
to admire the moon.

00:30:03.610 --> 00:30:04.780 line:80%
I came to see you, Mr. Mu.

00:30:10.866 --> 00:30:12.108 line:80%
Before I set out, I spread word

00:30:12.119 --> 00:30:13.839 line:80%
that the Jade Sunflower had reappeared.

00:30:14.050 --> 00:30:15.570 line:80%
Nie Zhe and the men in black

00:30:15.570 --> 00:30:17.330 line:80%
have been relentlessly pursuing it.

00:30:18.940 --> 00:30:20.570 line:80%
They should've reached nearby by now.

00:30:20.570 --> 00:30:22.290 line:80%
Nie Zhe caused the Chang massacre.

00:30:23.090 --> 00:30:24.330 line:80%
His crimes are unforgivable.

00:30:24.330 --> 00:30:25.523 line:80%
Naturally, he can't be spared.

00:30:25.980 --> 00:30:26.820 line:80%
However,

00:30:27.500 --> 00:30:28.850 line:80%
capturing Nie Zhe is one matter.

00:30:28.850 --> 00:30:30.980 line:80%
Zhao and I are only here
to pay respects.

00:30:30.980 --> 00:30:32.890 line:80%
Don't put her in a difficult position.

00:30:33.220 --> 00:30:34.500 line:80%
If her reputation is harmed,

00:30:35.890 --> 00:30:36.740 line:80%
it would not be good.

00:30:37.050 --> 00:30:38.290 line:80%
Rumors about you and Zhao

00:30:38.290 --> 00:30:39.610 line:80%
are spreading everywhere.

00:30:40.940 --> 00:30:42.740 line:80%
Does that not affect her reputation?

00:30:43.090 --> 00:30:44.330 line:80%
Song, don't forget.

00:30:44.850 --> 00:30:45.690 line:80%
You are

00:30:46.700 --> 00:30:47.980 line:80%
already betrothed.

00:30:48.780 --> 00:30:50.090 line:80%
I'll handle my betrothal.

00:30:51.220 --> 00:30:52.500 line:80%
No need for you to worry.

00:30:52.500 --> 00:30:53.406 line:80%
How will you handle it?

00:30:53.810 --> 00:30:55.570 line:80%
You shouldn't forget

00:30:55.570 --> 00:30:57.660 line:80%
that Zhao also has a fiancé,

00:30:57.660 --> 00:30:59.050 line:80%
Zhou Yuqi.

00:31:04.810 --> 00:31:05.810 line:80%
I accept

00:31:09.130 --> 00:31:09.980 line:80%
your return gift.

00:31:15.980 --> 00:31:17.180 line:80%
Gaogu Jade can't compare

00:31:18.220 --> 00:31:20.810 line:80%
to the rare stones you gifted.

00:31:21.130 --> 00:31:22.123 line:80%
It's good that you know.

00:31:29.540 --> 00:31:30.580 line:80%
(Kind and Hospitable)

00:31:30.580 --> 00:31:31.850 line:80%
It's hard to imagine

00:31:32.500 --> 00:31:33.940 line:80%
that we'd actually live

00:31:33.940 --> 00:31:36.180 line:80%
under the same roof as the demonic sect

00:31:36.610 --> 00:31:37.890 line:80%
at peace one day.

00:31:38.660 --> 00:31:39.890 line:80%
We are only staying a few days.

00:31:40.370 --> 00:31:42.123 line:80%
If they harbor no ill intent this time,

00:31:42.134 --> 00:31:43.573 line:80%
and both sides refrain from conflict,

00:31:43.740 --> 00:31:44.889 line:80%
that may not be a bad thing.

00:31:45.050 --> 00:31:46.070 line:80%
Have you forgotten, Yuzhi?

00:31:46.570 --> 00:31:48.660 line:80%
They nearly killed Master not long ago.

00:31:48.660 --> 00:31:50.130 line:80%
Such insidious and cunning people

00:31:50.570 --> 00:31:52.130 line:80%
can't be judged by appearances.

00:31:52.780 --> 00:31:53.620 line:80%
Fengchi, don't worry.

00:31:54.530 --> 00:31:55.470 line:80%
I've made arrangements.

00:31:56.260 --> 00:31:57.250 line:80%
After tomorrow,

00:31:57.500 --> 00:31:58.570 line:80%
you'll know.

00:31:59.180 --> 00:32:00.020 line:80%
Good.

00:32:00.500 --> 00:32:01.533 line:80%
We'll wait until tomorrow.

00:32:04.370 --> 00:32:05.210 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:32:06.220 --> 00:32:07.740 line:80%
I've written to inform Master.

00:32:07.740 --> 00:32:10.570 line:80%
In a few days,
he should send instructions.

00:32:10.570 --> 00:32:11.890 line:80%
I wonder what Father would think

00:32:11.890 --> 00:32:14.050 line:80%
if he knew Cai Zhao

00:32:14.050 --> 00:32:15.090 line:80%
and Mu Qingyan

00:32:15.890 --> 00:32:17.130 line:80%
were still entangled.

00:32:18.890 --> 00:32:19.730 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:32:22.130 --> 00:32:23.500 line:80%
I have something to say to you.

00:32:28.290 --> 00:32:30.090 line:80%
Zhou Yuqi and Min Xinrou are here.

00:32:30.090 --> 00:32:30.930 line:80%
I'll go receive them.

00:32:32.530 --> 00:32:33.500 line:80%
Then I'll go practice.

00:32:45.700 --> 00:32:46.540 line:80%
Zhao.

00:32:49.850 --> 00:32:50.690 line:80%
You two talk.

00:33:00.530 --> 00:33:01.370 line:80%
Yuqi,

00:33:01.610 --> 00:33:02.450 line:80%
sit.

00:33:05.130 --> 00:33:06.460 line:80%
Is Min feeling better?

00:33:07.370 --> 00:33:08.220 line:80%
Much better.

00:33:08.220 --> 00:33:09.060 line:80%
She has gone to rest.

00:33:24.180 --> 00:33:25.020 line:80%
Zhao,

00:33:25.420 --> 00:33:27.370 line:80%
did I do something to anger you?

00:33:30.740 --> 00:33:32.850 line:80%
If you mind
that I'm too close to Xinrou,

00:33:32.850 --> 00:33:34.530 line:80%
I'll keep my distance in the future.

00:33:34.530 --> 00:33:36.020 line:80%
But don't blame her because of it.

00:33:38.370 --> 00:33:40.220 line:80%
I no longer mind that matter.

00:33:41.780 --> 00:33:42.620 line:80%
That is good.

00:33:42.890 --> 00:33:44.052 line:80%
Then there will no longer be

00:33:44.063 --> 00:33:45.290 line:80%
those irrelevant people

00:33:45.290 --> 00:33:46.220 line:80%
coming to bother you.

00:33:50.090 --> 00:33:50.930 line:80%
What was that sound?

00:33:51.530 --> 00:33:52.740 line:80%
Most likely a stray cat.

00:33:53.290 --> 00:33:54.130 line:80%
A stray cat?

00:33:57.130 --> 00:33:59.220 line:80%
Quite a mischievous one.

00:33:59.610 --> 00:34:00.660 line:80%
It's asking for a beating.

00:34:04.460 --> 00:34:05.300 line:80%
You filthy cat.

00:34:05.530 --> 00:34:06.370 line:80%
Behave yourself.

00:34:09.410 --> 00:34:11.060 line:80%
Though I don't mind Miss Min,

00:34:11.060 --> 00:34:12.450 line:80%
the marriage between us

00:34:12.970 --> 00:34:14.180 line:80%
can indeed be postponed.

00:34:15.970 --> 00:34:17.580 line:80%
I'm not ready to marry yet.

00:34:19.700 --> 00:34:21.450 line:80%
Do you wish to postpone it,

00:34:21.450 --> 00:34:23.220 line:80%
or do you not wish to marry me at all?

00:34:24.410 --> 00:34:25.250 line:80%
Yuqi,

00:34:25.970 --> 00:34:27.220 line:80%
I need to avenge Uncle Chang

00:34:28.490 --> 00:34:30.060 line:80%
and help Yuzhi clear his poison.

00:34:30.060 --> 00:34:30.970 line:80%
That's too much for me.

00:34:31.660 --> 00:34:33.490 line:80%
I don't wish

00:34:33.490 --> 00:34:34.740 line:80%
to rush into marriage.

00:34:44.700 --> 00:34:45.646 line:80%
Break off the betrothal?

00:34:47.700 --> 00:34:49.490 line:80%
I've asked my father to propose it.

00:34:49.970 --> 00:34:51.220 line:80%
But the timing

00:34:52.370 --> 00:34:53.210 line:80%
is up to you.

00:34:53.490 --> 00:34:54.930 line:80%
What if I don't agree?

00:34:54.930 --> 00:34:55.780 line:80%
I'm willing to wait.

00:34:55.780 --> 00:34:57.140 line:80%
Then wait a lifetime.

00:35:01.780 --> 00:35:03.193 line:80%
You must be tired from the journey.

00:35:03.700 --> 00:35:04.890 line:80%
You should rest.

00:35:05.740 --> 00:35:06.580 line:80%
Please return.

00:35:25.660 --> 00:35:27.620 line:80%
Is this relentless entanglement

00:35:28.140 --> 00:35:29.180 line:80%
meaningful?

00:35:29.540 --> 00:35:31.060 line:80%
You are not me.

00:35:31.060 --> 00:35:32.780 line:80%
How do you know my joy?

00:35:33.660 --> 00:35:35.620 line:80%
As the Chief,

00:35:35.620 --> 00:35:36.970 line:80%
you bear heavy responsibility.

00:35:36.970 --> 00:35:38.580 line:80%
Can't you consider the greater good?

00:35:42.890 --> 00:35:44.660 line:80%
My father was best

00:35:44.660 --> 00:35:46.850 line:80%
at considering the greater good.

00:35:47.700 --> 00:35:48.740 line:80%
And the result?

00:35:51.490 --> 00:35:52.540 line:80%
With me here,

00:35:53.850 --> 00:35:54.930 line:80%
you will not marry Zhou.

00:36:01.970 --> 00:36:03.010 line:80%
Zhao,

00:36:03.010 --> 00:36:04.543 line:80%
I'll never miss what I seek all my life

00:36:05.100 --> 00:36:08.100 line:80%
and endure in silence forever

00:36:08.100 --> 00:36:09.410 line:80%
like my father.

00:36:12.860 --> 00:36:17.850 line:80%
♪You come to my dreams again♪

00:36:19.180 --> 00:36:25.210 line:80%
♪On this cold day, drunk with wine♪

00:36:27.180 --> 00:36:33.930 line:80%
♪Life shifts, a thousand faces pass by♪

00:36:36.140 --> 00:36:37.410 line:80%
Where is the dice I gave you?

00:36:38.330 --> 00:36:39.170 line:80%
Do you still have it?

00:36:43.970 --> 00:36:44.983 line:80%
I threw it away long ago.

00:36:47.900 --> 00:36:54.890 line:80%
♪Across rivers and mountains,
I roam free and wide♪

00:36:59.810 --> 00:37:01.180 line:80%
(As long as I live,)

00:37:02.490 --> 00:37:03.330 line:80%
(I will never)

00:37:04.660 --> 00:37:06.450 line:80%
(let go of you.)

00:37:15.140 --> 00:37:15.980 line:80%
Zhao.

00:37:19.810 --> 00:37:21.060 line:80%
I did not see you at dinner.

00:37:21.540 --> 00:37:22.380 line:80%
No appetite?

00:37:24.620 --> 00:37:27.290 line:80%
You've been so attentive lately.

00:37:27.301 --> 00:37:29.621 line:80%
Nothing like the you who went
to the demonic sect with me.

00:37:31.660 --> 00:37:33.370 line:80%
When we went to the Youming Path,

00:37:33.370 --> 00:37:34.930 line:80%
I shouldn't have focused only on myself

00:37:34.930 --> 00:37:36.060 line:80%
and neglected you.

00:37:36.060 --> 00:37:37.260 line:80%
I'll be mindful in the future.

00:37:38.060 --> 00:37:38.900 line:80%
I'm not important.

00:37:39.450 --> 00:37:41.220 line:80%
Just take good care of Lingbo.

00:37:43.740 --> 00:37:45.176 line:80%
I've spoken frankly with Lingbo.

00:37:45.187 --> 00:37:46.947 line:80%
When we return,
I'll dissolve the betrothal.

00:37:50.660 --> 00:37:51.620 line:80%
Zhao,

00:37:55.140 --> 00:37:55.980 line:80%
I...

00:37:57.401 --> 00:38:08.061 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:38:26.821 --> 00:38:31.231 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:38:31.796 --> 00:38:36.411 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:38:36.751 --> 00:38:41.316 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:38:41.841 --> 00:38:46.141 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:38:49.086 --> 00:38:53.786 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:38:54.311 --> 00:38:58.601 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:38:59.261 --> 00:39:03.291 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:39:03.606 --> 00:39:08.731 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:39:09.306 --> 00:39:14.116 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:39:14.331 --> 00:39:18.501 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:39:19.226 --> 00:39:23.161 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:39:23.661 --> 00:39:28.936 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

00:39:51.666 --> 00:39:56.796 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:39:57.161 --> 00:40:01.531 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:40:01.796 --> 00:40:05.926 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:40:06.111 --> 00:40:11.686 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪